<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFC8FF8EFD059654FCA5F2CE" box="[668,825,3400,3433]" name="Philippines" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">Philippines</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion id="5E52F847FFC8FF8EFCD79654FC5DF2CE" box="[846,961,3400,3433]" country="Philippines" name="Palawan" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">Palawan</collectingRegion>
&amp; Calamian Is). H. b. rajah Thomas, 1921 — Borneo.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9C2936A5FFC8FF8EFA179A34F85CFEEE" blockId="4.[1416,2622,296,1553]" box="[1422,1984,296,329]" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">
